ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2011-12
PrecisAppointment of DAVID COLLINS as Ambassador of Canada to the Arab Republic of South Sudan, resident in Nairobi; CHANTAL de VARENNES as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Liberia, with residence in Abidjan; KENNETH MACARTNEY as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Sweden; JOHN MORRISON as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Estonia and the Republic of Lithuania, with residence in Riga; and L. PHILIPPE RHEAULT as Consul General of Canada in Chongqing, People's Republic of China.
